## 🧠 Simulation Overview

* Humans:

  * Start with health = 100 and random age
  * Move up to 4 steps
* Vampires:

  * Move up to 8 steps
  * Infect humans
* Items:

  * Food (+30 health)
  * Water (+50 health)
  * Garlic (+100 health)

(From your implementation )

